36
00:03:07,990 --> 00:03:09,790
So if you don't truly love it,

37
00:03:10,150 --> 00:03:11,510
you should quit as soon as possible.

38
00:03:19,390 --> 00:03:20,550
Excuse me.

39
00:03:26,870 --> 00:03:28,150
