100
00:06:08,030 --> 00:06:08,790
Add her on WeChat.

101
00:06:08,790 --> 00:06:09,590
Are you...

102
00:06:10,710 --> 00:06:11,990
Still, accept my friend request.

103
00:06:13,710 --> 00:06:14,550
No, it's really...

104
00:06:15,670 --> 00:06:16,590
Hey, you...

105
00:06:16,590 --> 00:06:18,470
