107
00:06:31,670 --> 00:06:32,590
What's going on?

108
00:06:32,590 --> 00:06:33,230
Shut up!

109
00:06:38,909 --> 00:06:40,030
Don't say a word.

110
00:06:52,710 --> 00:06:53,470
Hello?

111
