220
00:12:30,990 --> 00:12:32,070
Isn't it fashionable?

221
00:12:40,510 --> 00:12:41,230
Fine.

222
00:12:43,070 --> 00:12:44,870
We got even, all right?

223
00:12:46,750 --> 00:12:48,110
How about this?

224
00:12:48,510 --> 00:12:49,350
Well,

225
00:12:50,310 --> 00:12:51,230
