277
00:15:33,870 --> 00:15:34,990
shoot videos,

278
00:15:34,990 --> 00:15:36,710
or edit videos.

279
00:15:36,990 --> 00:15:37,710
You are also like this.

280
00:15:37,710 --> 00:15:38,950
You either take on projects,

281
00:15:38,950 --> 00:15:40,110
shoot videos,

